name: STRS (instrumental)
description: this the instrumental for STRS, a track i made around september/october 2020. This was made with a combination of Ableton stock sounds, pads and synths/ virtual instruments from arturia/analog lab, and engineered in Logic Pro. I was going thru a lot from falling in love with someone i couldn't date at the time, dealing with repercussions from unrequited love of a former best-friend, and delusions and psychosis from weed. i'm proud to be able to continue my journey and reflect on how hard my journey was. 2021 taught me more than i could ever imagine about my internals and where i am headed to go. last piece of 2021.
